trans-unit.source: Performs a cryptographic transformation of data using the Rijndael algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Utfører en kryptografisk transformering data med algoritmen Rijndael.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Using this class is not recommended.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE]> Ved hjelp av denne klassen anbefales ikke.

trans-unit.source: A better practice is to use <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> with a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object.
trans-unit.target: Det er lurt bedre å bruke <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>med en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object handles the padding issues that can occur when using RijndaelManagedTransform directly.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet behandler utfylling problemene som kan forekomme når du bruker RijndaelManagedTransform direkte.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>

trans-unit.source: For an example, see the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se et eksempel se <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>

trans-unit.source: Both the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A> methods return an instance of the RijndaelManagedTransform class that is initialized with the key information of the current <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> object.
trans-unit.target: Både den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A>og <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A>metoder returnere en forekomst av klassen RijndaelManagedTransform er initialisert med nøkkelinformasjon for gjeldende <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A>

trans-unit.source: To encrypt or decrypt data using the Rijndael algorithm, pass the RijndaelManagedTransform object returned by these methods to a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object.
trans-unit.target: For å kryptere eller dekryptere dataene ved hjelp av algoritmen Rijndael, kan du sende RijndaelManagedTransform-objekt som er returnert av disse metodene til en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This method is a simple call to <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er et enkelt kall til <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>klasse.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Calling `Dispose` allows the resources used by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> to be reallocated for other purposes.
trans-unit.target: Kaller `Dispose` tillater ressursene som brukes av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>til tildeles på nytt til andre formål.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: For more information about `Dispose`, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om `Dispose`, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.
trans-unit.target: Kall `Dispose` når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden forlater den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall `Dispose`, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>ble bruker.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall `Dispose` før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: Resets the internal state of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> so it can be used again to do a different encryption or decryption.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller den interne tilstanden til <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> slik at den kan brukes på nytt til å utføre en annen kryptering eller dekryptering.

trans-unit.source: The Reset method is called automatically when you call <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Metoden tilbakestilling kalles automatisk når du kaller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Reset method is not called when, for example, the encrypted input data is garbage and cannot be decrypted.
trans-unit.target: Metoden tilbakestilling kalles ikke når, for eksempel krypterte inndataene er ugyldige og kan ikke dekrypteres.

trans-unit.source: In this case, an exception is thrown and Reset is not called.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet et unntak, og tilbakestille kalles ikke.

trans-unit.source: You can choose to manually call the Reset method in this case.
trans-unit.target: Du kan velge å kalle manuelt tilbakestilling-metoden i dette tilfellet.
